### Description

Inheritance was broken somewhere between 15.0.4 and 15.1.4.

Consider base class:

```ts
@Directive()
export abstract class BaseComponent {
   protected readonly extra: any;
    
   constructor() {
       this.extra = 'this is a test';
   }
}
```

Inherited class:

```ts
@Component({
    selector: '[ChildComponent]',
    templateUrl: './component.html'
})
export class ChildComponent extends BaseComponent {
    protected declare readonly extra: object; // type changed to object

    constructor() {
       super();
       window.console.log(this.extra); // this no longer outputs value from parent
   }
}
```

After update to 15.1.4 `ChildComponent` has empty `extra` value.

